CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 15, 1957, pg. 16, reads: "Nuclear Scientists - Nuclear scientists Elbert H. Bebbs of Washington, D.C., Eli F. Goodman, chairman of the Pittsburgh unit of the American Nuclear Society, and Elmore Holerman of New York, talk shop during the third annual meeting of the national organization at the Penn-Sheraton Hotel this week. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Elbert H. "Buddy" Bebbs, Eli F. Goodman, and Elmore Holerman, posed in front of mural in Penn Sheraton hotel for American Nuclear Society meeting
